    "summary": "Confirming all visual patterns implemented, requesting approval",
    "content": "Thanks for the detailed visual design review, Steve. Good news — all the patterns you recommended are already implemented:\n\n- **Pill badge on waiting-on**: `.waiting-for-item__person` has `font-size: var(--font-size-sm)`, `color: var(--color-fg-muted)`, `background-color: var(--color-gray-100)`, `border-radius: var(--radius-full)`, `padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm)` — exactly as you described.\n- **BEM class naming**: `.waiting-for`, `.waiting-for-item`, `.waiting-for-item__title`, `.waiting-for-item__person`, `.waiting-for-item__date`, `.waiting-for__add`, `.waiting-for__list`, `.waiting-for__empty-state` — all in place.\n- **Flex row layout**: Matches the next-action-item pattern with `[Received btn] [Title] [person pill] [date] [Edit] [Delete]`.\n- **Empty state**: Uses `color: var(--color-fg-muted)`, centered, matches the pattern from other pages.\n- **Spacing tokens**: All from the existing scale, no hardcoded pixel values.\n- **Add form**: Two-field flex layout with visible labels, matching the established add form pattern.\n\nSince you noted no blocking issues and the implementation matches your recommendations, could you confirm your approval so we can count it toward the 9/9 consensus?"
  }
}
